This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the ai21labs organization:
- ai21labs/AI21-Jamba2-Mini tokenizer.json
- ai21labs/AI21-Jamba2-3B tokenizer.json (same tokenizer family as AI21-Jamba2-Mini)
- ai21labs/AI21-Jamba-Reasoning-3B tokenizer.json (same tokenizer family as AI21-Jamba2-Mini)
- ai21labs/Jamba-v0.1 tokenizer.json

